OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FScotland's NHS has been hit with a
OL,8,F"devastating collapse in care
OL,9,Fstandards", with patients "routinely
OL,10,Fcoming to harm" and unable to access
OL,11,Fbasic services, a report by the Royal
OL,12,FCollege of Nursing (RCN) has found.
OL,14,FThe nursing union said "demoralised"
OL,15,Fstaff across the nation's hospitals
OL,16,Fhave witnessed patients going into
OL,17,Fcardiac arrest while forced to lay in
OL,18,Fcorridors due to a lack of beds.
