OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe RCN said there was a "corridor
OL,8,Fcare crisis" in hospitals across the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,FIts survey of NHS staff includes
OL,12,Ftestimonies from more than 5,000
OL,13,Fnurses in the UK, with 500 of those
OL,14,Fbeing from Scotland.
OL,16,FThe RCN said its 400-page report must
OL,17,Fbe a "wake-up call" for the country's
OL,18,Fpolitical leaders.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@LO]yD@FOUyD@SO]
