OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIts report found staff in Scotland are
OL,8,Fcaring for multiple patients in a
OL,9,Fsingle corridor and unable to access
OL,10,Foxygen, cardiac monitors, suction and
OL,11,Fother lifesaving equipment.
OL,13,FThey say patients are being left with
OL,14,Fno access to bathroom facilities or
OL,15,Fbuzzers, with nurses forced to deliver
OL,16,Fpersonal care to incontinent patients
OL,17,Fwith no privacy.
OL,19,FNine in 10 of those surveyed said
OL,20,Fpatient safety is being compromised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
