OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FA Scottish nurse said: "Department
OL,8,Fwith capacity for 13 beds, we had 40
OL,9,Fin, with patients on chairs having
OL,10,Ftreatments administered, also sitting
OL,11,Fin the waiting room on cardiac
OL,12,Fmonitors, using privacy screens to put
OL,13,Faround patients to use the bedpan."
OL,15,FOne unnamed member of staff said they
OL,16,Fwere forced to clean an elderly
OL,17,Fincontinent patient in the charge
OL,18,Fnurse's office.
