OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FAnother added: "A very confused
OL,8,Fpatient was brought to the corridor.
OL,9,FThis patient wandered the corridors
OL,10,Fand was found in different areas of
OL,11,Fthe ward multiple times.
OL,13,F"A bed was eventually found in a
OL,14,Ftemporary area which was an office
OL,15,Fusually used for out-patients
OL,16,Fappointments, it still had the
OL,17,Fcomputer desk set up and had no window
OL,18,For toilet."
