OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FA nursing support worker said: "My
OL,8,Flast shift, I went into a full ward
OL,9,Fand 34 patients were referred to come
OL,10,Finto the ward, 10 of which were in the
OL,11,Fcorridor already waiting.
OL,13,F"One of the patients had a stroke,
OL,14,Fanother with an increased oxygen
OL,15,Frequirement and several with the flu.
OL,16,FExtremely unsafe as patients kept on
OL,17,Farriving with nowhere to move our
OL,18,Falready admitted patients to."
