OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe RCN, the UK's largest nursing
OL,8,Funion, said staffing levels have not
OL,9,Fbeen increased to cover the rise in
OL,10,Fpatient numbers.
OL,12,FThe scale of the issue, the report
OL,13,Fstated, has prompted concerns about
OL,14,Finfection prevention and control as
OL,15,Fpatients are "crammed into tight
OL,16,Fspaces next to one another".
