OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FOne nurse said: "Flu-positive patients
OL,8,Fare being transferred to wards before
OL,9,Frooms become available. Patients with
OL,10,Fflu then being cared for in ward
OL,11,Fcorridors next to other vulnerable
OL,12,Fpatients."
OL,14,FThe RCN said corridor care has become
OL,15,Fnormalised in NHS hospitals across the
OL,16,FUK, as nursing staff report elderly
OL,17,Fand vulnerable patients receiving
OL,18,F"undignified and unsafe" treatment.
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@JO]zD@AOUzD@XO]
