OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FAlmost seven in 10 (66.81%) nurses
OL,8,Fsurveyed reported delivering care in
OL,9,Fovercrowded or unsuitable places `
OL,10,Flike corridors, offices, converted
OL,11,Fcupboards and even car parks ` on a
OL,12,Fdaily basis.
OL,14,FRCN Scotland director Colin Poolman
OL,15,Fsaid: "This report makes for
OL,16,Fdistressing reading and should be a
OL,17,Fwake-up call for the Scottish
OL,18,FGovernment.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
