OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F302A1737012767
OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"The impact goes far beyond the doors
OL,8,Fof emergency departments, with nursing
OL,9,Fstaff across many acute settings
OL,10,Fdesperately struggling as they are
OL,11,Fforced to create space in clinical
OL,12,Fareas for additional unstaffed beds or
OL,13,Fprovide patient care in corridors and
OL,14,Fother inappropriate locations.
OL,16,F"This is completely unacceptable for
OL,17,Fpatient safety and staff wellbeing. No
OL,18,Fpatient should ever have to suffer the
OL,19,Frisk or indignity of being cared for
OL,20,Fin such a way ` yet it has been
OL,21,Fallowed to become normal practice.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
