OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F302A1737012767
OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"The Scottish Government must commit
OL,8,Fto publishing the data on exactly how
OL,9,Fmany patients are being cared for in
OL,10,Fthese circumstances. The public
OL,11,Fdeserves to know what is happening to
OL,12,Fpatient safety.
OL,14,F"They must also commit to long-term
OL,15,Faction and investment focused on
OL,16,Faddressing the nursing workforce
OL,17,Fshortages and building sustainable
OL,18,Fcapacity both within in the NHS and,
OL,19,Fmost importantly, within community and
OL,20,Fsocial care."
