OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FBritish Medical Association chair of
OL,8,Fcouncil Professor Philip Banfield
OL,9,Fsaid: "Corridor care should never ever
OL,10,Fbe 'the norm' in any hospital and yet,
OL,11,Fas this report reveals, our patients
OL,12,Fare being looked after, not in beds,
OL,13,Fon wards or in proper cubicles, but in
OL,14,Fplaces which are unsafe and inhumane.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
