OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Doctors, and now our nursing
OL,8,Fcolleagues, are almost beyond despair
OL,9,Fas they struggle with the impossible
OL,10,Ftask of trying vainly to look after
OL,11,Fscores of sick and dying people, left
OL,12,Ffor hours on end in unsanitary and
OL,13,Funacceptable conditions."
OL,15,FScottish Conservative health
OL,16,Fspokesperson Dr Sandesh Gulhane MSP
OL,17,Fsaid: "This devastating report must be
OL,18,Fan urgent wake-up call for SNP
OL,19,Fministers.
