OL,3,C'Devastating collapse in standards' in
OL,4,CNHS amid 'corridor care crisis' `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"The scandalous failure of successive
OL,8,FSNP health secretaries has left nurses
OL,9,Fto deal with complete chaos in
OL,10,Fhospital corridors."
OL,12,FScottish Labour Health spokeswoman
OL,13,FDame Jackie Baillie said: "This
OL,14,Fharrowing report is a reminder of how
OL,15,Ffar standards have fallen on the SNP's
OL,16,Fwatch.
OL,18,F"Our nurses are as hard-working and
OL,19,Fcommitted as ever, but they cannot
OL,20,Fdefend the NHS against the SNP's
OL,21,Fmismanagement forever."
