OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHealth Secretary Neil Gray said: "I
OL,8,Fwant to apologise to anyone whose
OL,9,Fexperience of the NHS has fallen short
OL,10,Fof the standards we all expect from
OL,11,Four health service.
OL,13,F"A&E departments are under pressure
OL,14,Fdue to high occupancy and delays with
OL,15,Fpatients who need extra support before
OL,16,Fgoing home, which affects the flow of
OL,17,Fpatients from A&E to inpatient wards.
OL,19,F"But we are determined to drive
OL,20,Fimprovements, reduce waiting lists and
OL,21,Ftackle delayed discharge."
